articles.title: Test 1
articles.name: test1_collada_MasterJSON
articles.content: The file named test 1 is a building next to the university oval stadium. This building is a feature without any textures because the cityGML export is a geometry export. The master json is named test1_geometry_MasterJSON.json. I must delete this file because we can have the textures now.

articles.title: Test 2
articles.name: test2_collada_MasterJSON
articles.content: The file named test 2 is all the buildings of the university. These buildings are gather in one feature without any textures because the cityGML export is a geometry export. The master json is named test2_geometry_MasterJSON.json. I must delete this file because we can have the textures and multi features now.

articles.title: Test 3
articles.name: test3_collada_MasterJSON
articles.content: The file named test 3 is some buildings in Berlin, Germany. These buildings are several features with textures because the cityGML export is a collada/Gltf export. The master json is named test3_collada_MasterJSON.json. I must keep this file because it works very well.
